{"tid":600532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺連登好多廢柴鍾意透過踩啲社會最底層來出氣","createTime":"2018-03-21T11:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T11:32:26.000Z","uid":76115,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"316c30d1e5a08eed1f7f3ce4a3f0cac8288d532b","tid":600532,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱好搵到過萬幾就話好憎萬幾都搵唔到個班, 自己交&quot;好多&quot;稅養埋班窮人<br />\n<br />\n自己成世無樣野叻過, 好在啱啱好係個正常人唔使讀特殊學校, 就成日開post話啲弱智人士、自閉人士、精神病人係渣滓要人道毀滅<br />\n<br />\n怯者憤怒抽刀向更弱者, 真係好撚中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27097e98c5e43a23f6caca35e80f2dd90268b9ea","tid":600532,"uid":40470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本連登仔先係社會最底層<br />\n<br />\n讀ive<br />\n<br />\n搵20000以下<br />\n<br />\n住公屋<br />\n<br />\n溝唔到女<br />\n<br />\n樣衰<br />\n<br />\n當然唔係全部連登仔都係以上咁<br />\n<br />\n不過都有一半以上係呢類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf7db1260f4178613485eb8b5570bf2abab793e","tid":600532,"uid":26952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/192601_70483dad8faa5c5e5969902c962b22a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F192601_70483dad8faa5c5e5969902c962b22a3.png&h=5c1993f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86008d7c8d29e671d0b0e79bfb901a125d2d64e","tid":600532,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"窮人係自卑㗎啦<br />\n所以咪做唔到大事囉<br />\n成世做廢青"},{"pid":"6c13fa6f5c66a6362578b6ae476eb5bdc09d2e18","tid":600532,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T